  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们来画一个用户登录的完整时序图吧。核心流程是：用户在页面提交邮箱和密码，前端把请求发给AuthService，然后AuthService去数据库查用户。这里要分两种情况处理——邮箱不存在，或者邮箱存在但密码不对，这两种都要返回401。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Frontend",
        "AuthService",
        "Database",
        "email",
        "password",
        "401 Unauthorized"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，两个失败分支。那登录成功之后呢？AuthService需要创建session吧，是用UUID来标识会话吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AuthService",
        "UUID",
        "session"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，成功时AuthService生成UUID作为session ID，存到Database，然后给前端返回201和Set-Cookie。前端拿到cookie后把用户重定向到dashboard。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AuthService",
        "Database",
        "UUID",
        "201 Created",
        "Set-Cookie",
        "Frontend",
        "dashboard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主流程和第一个alt分支——邮箱找不到的情况。User提交凭证给Frontend，Frontend POST到AuthService，AuthService查询Database，如果返回Not found，就一路401回去，最后Frontend给用户显示错误。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Frontend",
        "AuthService",
        "Database",
        "POST /sessions",
        "Not found",
        "401 Unauthorized",
        "Show error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
