      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "嵌套alt画好了。密码验证通过的话，AuthService调用Database创建session并传入UUID，然后返回201 Created带Set-Cookie给Frontend，Frontend最后Redirect User到dashboard。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AuthService",
        "Database",
        "Create session",
